### Estefanini Serverless API - Almacenar

# Variables de entorno para el archivo
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/dev
@prodUrl = https://mxipk20k2a.execute-api.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/dev
@apiKey = your-api-key-here

### ========================================
### ENDPOINTS DE DESARROLLO LOCAL (sin API key)
### ========================================

### 1. Almacenar - POST (Crear Custom Warrior - local)
POST {{baseUrl}}/almacenar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Shadow Ninja",
  "powerLevel": 850,
  "height": 1.75,
  "weight": 70,
  "abilities": ["Stealth", "Shadow Clone", "Ninja Arts"],
  "species": "Human-Ninja",
  "description": "A mysterious warrior trained in the ancient arts of stealth and combat",
  "createdBy": "jonathan@example.com"
}

### ========================================
### ENDPOINTS DE PRODUCCIÓN (con API key y rate-limiting)
### ========================================

### 2. Almacenar - POST (producción con API key)
POST {{prodUrl}}/almacenar
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "name": "Cyber Warrior",
  "powerLevel": 950,
  "height": 1.80,
  "weight": 75,
  "abilities": ["Cyber Enhancement", "Digital Strike", "Data Analysis"],
  "species": "Human-Cyborg",
  "description": "A warrior enhanced with cybernetic implants",
  "createdBy": "user@example.com"
}